{
  "chapter": 25,
  "chapter_summary": "本章承接前文，黄鲁直重伤倒地后说出最后一句\"我绝不会看错你\"，雄娘子深受感动，跪地磕头后狂奔而去。楚留香跟踪雄娘子至山区，发现他进入一个洞穴，洞穴竟是通往神水宫的秘径。雄娘子在洞中换上女装易容，楚留香才发觉他竟是绝世美男子，易容术精妙绝伦。雄娘子用黑色皮囊充气制成皮筏，欲顺流入神水宫，却被暗中之人击破皮筏。此时宫南燕乘轻舟从迷雾中出现，拦住雄娘子。两人在幽秘绝谷中展开一段暧昧对话，宫南燕提起雄娘子昔日所立毒誓，并向他表露爱意。雄娘子虽有好感却婉拒，表示不能害了她，称她永远温柔纯洁可爱。楚留香在暗中旁听，感慨雄娘子对女人的手段高明。本章揭示了雄娘子与宫南燕之间微妙的情感关系，以及雄娘子与神水宫的深层联系。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_lu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "黄鲁直",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我绝不会看错你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "雄娘子",
      "listener": "char_huang_lu_zhi",
      "text": "我对不起你。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他……他这是什么意思?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "他这只不过是想入神水宫，因为无论他女儿是生是死，也要见她最后一面，但他也知道黄鲁直绝不会让他去的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "因为他此去必死无疑，黄鲁直不忍眼看他去送死。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "正是如此，所以我一定要跟他一起入宫，戴老前辈和黄老剑客，就全都交给你了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "莫忘了，还有蓉儿。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来他是要用这皮囊作皮筏，然后再乘着皮筏顺流而下，直入神水宫。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "宫南燕",
      "listener": "char_xiong_niang_zi",
      "text": "你既已来了，何必走呢?",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "雄娘子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来是你。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "宫南燕",
      "listener": "char_xiong_niang_zi",
      "text": "不错，是我，你想不到吧!但我早已知道你会来的，早就在这里等着你了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "雄娘子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我本来也不想来的，可是，我非来一趟不可。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "宫南燕",
      "listener": "char_xiong_niang_zi",
      "text": "你难道已忘记了你昔日立下的毒誓么?",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "宫南燕",
      "listener": "char_xiong_niang_zi",
      "text": "对不起，我并不是有意要说出那些话来伤害你的，你莫要生我的气好吗?我……我下次一定不说了。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "宫南燕",
      "listener": "char_xiong_niang_zi",
      "text": "这就是你本来面目么?难怪她总是说我长得很像你，甚至比你的女儿还像你……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "雄娘子",
      "listener": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "text": "她……她时常在你面前说起我?",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "宫南燕",
      "listener": "char_xiong_niang_zi",
      "text": "嗯!",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "宫南燕",
      "listener": "char_xiong_niang_zi",
      "text": "你也时常想起她么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "雄娘子",
      "listener": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "text": "这些年来，我早已将什么人都忘了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "宫南燕",
      "listener": "char_xiong_niang_zi",
      "text": "好个薄情的人，别人为了你死去活来，你却将别人忘得干干净净，世上难道就真的没有一个人能令你动心的么?",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "雄娘子",
      "listener": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "宫南燕",
      "listener": "char_xiong_niang_zi",
      "text": "我现在才知道你实在是个迷死人的妖精，也难怪那么多女孩子心甘情愿的为你死，就连我……我也……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "雄娘子",
      "listener": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "text": "你也怎么样?",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "宫南燕",
      "listener": "char_xiong_niang_zi",
      "text": "别人都说你最了解女人，你难道就不了解我?难道还不明白我的心意?",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "雄娘子",
      "listener": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "text": "我还是不明白好些。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "宫南燕",
      "listener": "char_xiong_niang_zi",
      "text": "为什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "雄娘子",
      "listener": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "text": "因为你和别的女孩子不同，我不能……不能害了你。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "宫南燕",
      "listener": "char_xiong_niang_zi",
      "text": "我也是个女人，我也要……也要……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_niang_zi",
      "speaker_name": "雄娘子",
      "listener": "char_gong_nan_yan",
      "text": "在我眼中，你永远是那么温柔，那么纯洁，那么可爱，只要能远远望着你，我已心满意足了。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 348
    }
  ],
